pt.ua.dicoogle.sdk.settings.types

Class StaticDataTable

  • java.lang.Object
    • pt.ua.dicoogle.sdk.settings.types.DataTable
      • pt.ua.dicoogle.sdk.settings.types.StaticDataTable
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    GenericSetting

    public class StaticDataTable
extends DataTable
    Handles a data (type) that is suposed to be on a table form. Supports multiple fields per row. The contents of this table cannot be modified by the end user on the HTML interface.
